  "prompt": "I have been dream and thinking about this boy who's 1 year older than me and I never met him in my whole life .. does it mean he could be real?",
  "response": "Dreams and thoughts about people we have never met can sometimes be intriguing and mysterious. These dreams could be a reflection of your subconscious mind, your desires, or your imagination. They don't necessarily mean that the person is real or that you will meet them in the future. It's common for the mind to create scenarios and characters in dreams based on our feelings, experiences, and even influences from media or stories we've heard.\n\nIf you find yourself often thinking about or dreaming of this boy, it might be helpful to consider what qualities or attributes he represents to you and why he stands out in your dreams. This can provide insight into your own desires or thoughts. While it's an intriguing thought, there's no definitive evidence to suggest that dreaming about someone means they exist or that you will meet them in real life.",
